content: FINALLY! MY NUMBER ONE APP FOR ME. Forget the rest, I've had similar apps before but the became unavailable in app store. When I got a new phone it took me forever but I finally found it. This app is the best for recording my time spent at all of my customers for my landscaping route, automatically.
Easy to use when you know how to enter data easily.

This version has proven stable, as well as incredibly useful. Well worth the small price. In fact, you are getting much more for you money than you realize once you begin using the app. With regards to time tracking accountability and profitability, the plain truth is, the better you are at managing your time results in greater profits. This app will help you do that for sure. Thanks.
Please add settings for break time 45 min

This is a simple and easy to use app. However, it enables you to have available all the statistics you need. Recommended. Edited: I have now deleted all my other time recording apps and now exclusively use East Hours. The more I use it the more powerfu I find it to be. At the same time it is smple to use and accessible. Well done dev.
Easy to use, does what i need it to do, makes my life simpler. What more would I want?

A great way to keep track of your work time hours. Unfortunately does not automatically calculate time and a half for overtime. But I entered that in as a separate pay rate and with just a little bit of figuring was able to make that part of my calculations.
App allows me to track what I need. I needed something to track parts usage on my service calls for work and this fit the bill beautifully.
It's a useful tool
Simply brilliant
Wish the location was more accurate and its not clocking me out when i leave and clocking me in when im home

I really like this app for keeping track of care hours and duties. I only wish I could print out weekly/monthly/yearly totals. I love how simple it is and the colors sure do help with ease of access. Thank you for offering this app.
Fun to set schedule
This has been exactly what I need for keeping track of multiple activities. It's easy to use and easy to edit/modify.
Easy hours timesheet allows me to easily log my hours worked. I enjoy the ability to customize each position I hold. Great app to keep track of time worked.
I was quite satisfied untill now. I can't set the custom time range to any date from December 2019 to January 2020. Can you please fix this? Update: fixed by developer. Thank you!
replyContent: Thank you for reporting the bug.  We published a 9.4.2 release that addresses this custom time range issue and contains a variety of other improvements.

Great

Fantastic for keeping track of my hours worked. Very user friendly.
Quick simple easy to use. Does exactly what it's supposed to
Great app to keep track of hours

Alot of detailed options for tracking time
Great time keeping app
Excellent for keeping track of mutiple jobs and tasks

After using easy hr lite for a week i found it very useful and very easy to use.I brought the full version and im glad i did im keeping on top of my hrs at work thank you very much.From New Zealand Willz
easy to use, very handy for keeping track of pay as well, helps me adjust the number of hours I need to make up during the week as my start and end time can vary.
Best app for people who work at different places in one day. I'll give it 5 stars once the email can be sent.
The easiest and most comprehensive time management tool available. This app is awesome!
Love this app.
Really great so far. Just used it for a day & so far it's great in keeping track of everything.
good app works well

content: A+
Simply the easiest, most intuitive time sheet app I've ever used.

Initial thoughts on this are encouraging, it is easy to use and quick to start. I like the geo location and auto recording,  very useful. Not quite sure why the pie chart shows three different values as being equal, but hey ho. I hope to see more improvements and features in the future

Great app, really useful for keeping track of time spent on different jobs/projects. Especially like the automatic sign in.  Be useful to be able to track time on a project that is not billable (currently the only options are "billable" it "break").
It's pretty complex to learn but once you get how it works it's pretty effective.
Overall, a great app to keep track of the task you do at work.
replyContent: Thank you for the kind words.  Feel free to use the in app feedback if you have any additional ideas for improvements.

content: Now it logs in and out when it pleases. I had reported this issue as requested below and received no response.  I did so again yesterday.
replyContent: David, we checked through our email, including Junk/Spam folders, and unfortunately we do not see any emails about app issues.  Can you send us your Android Version, Device Model #, and Easy Hours Version to easyhours@30xi.com?  Thank you for your patience as we address your feedback.  We want to ensure you continue to love Easy Hours.

content: New version update: I've gone from 5 stars to 3! I hate the new UI. It no longer shows the day or date in the weekly or monthly views. Some me.us are overlaid with distracting graphics. My installation was automatically updated, so I didn't get a choice. If I could, I would gladly choose to go back to the previous version, which I loved.  On previous version: 5 stars I needed something to automatically track my time at work. I tried building my own, via Tasker, etc., but I'm  not a programmer and found I was simply over my head. Then I found Easy Hours! It does everything I dreamed of. Setup was just too simple. Kudos for all responsible for such a great product!
replyContent: Andy, thank you for your feedback. We encourage all customers to contact us directly for issues.  7.0 should resolve any issues you may have had with the prior menu layout.  Please give the updates a try.

content: Have had it a couple of months now and can't complain one bit about it. I use it to track multiple jobs I am working on. well worth the few dollars to buy it
This app is awesome keep track of work hrs + overtime

I use the app to track time and cost on multiple projects. Great easy to use interface and works well. I like the use of the Google Drive backup feature as well. Geofencing on my projects also works well and exporting my weeks work to excel isb easy.  Can't fault this app.

I tried this app and liked it a lot, so much that I had to write to the developers and let them know that I couldn't sync to Google Drive. That was the only thing stopping me from using it as my main time tracking app. My experience was a very pleasant one, they were very responsive and had the issue resolved quickly. I'll definitely recommend it to my friends.
Awesome thank you highly recommend
replyContent: Date restrictions have been removed in Easy Hours 5.0.  Thanks for your continued support.
